result.name: The Cheesecake Factory

reviews.text: Just as good as in the US, albeit pricier. The environment feels just like it does in America, and the food portions are very hearty. Our waitress was attentive and professional, and our food arrived quick after ordering. This is a great spot for a celebration meal; just be prepared to spend more than you might normally.

A American restaurant while most of the foreign waiters and waitresses are well trained but the local waitress are just so impolite. A waitress came on request and in two second asking we whether I will place order. “你唔係叫野食咩？”  , the way the serve the food is like banging the table. I just cannot believe how terrible is their service. 
Food size is huge so better be noticed

Amazing food as always. We first visited the cheese cake factory in the US and now in Hong Kong. Service and food standards are consistent! Delicious food, huge portions, reasonably priced. Cheese cake is divine, especially the new cinnabon version!!! Conveniently located inside the mall, waiting time was about an hour but well worth the wait!
Perfect example of good American food. You can't go wrong here. It is pricey though, so make sure you know that before heading over. It makes a good celebratory treat!

The food is good. This definitely satisfied my cravings for something sweet. Personally I find the servings too big for one person. The cheesecakes vary in character from the simple Classic cheesecake to extremely indulgent 30th Anniversary cheesecake which has layers of what seems to be cheesecake, caramel and fudge. There are also tangy cheesecakes like key lime and raspberry truffle. One downside for me is the long line, so try to come before peak hours such as lunch and dinner time, and I find the interiors too dark and outdated.

reviews.text: 份量十足🤣
不錯👍🏻

Just as good as in the US, albeit pricier. The environment feels just like it does in America, and the food portions are very hearty. Our waitress was attentive and professional, and our food arrived quick after ordering. This is a great spot for a celebration meal; just be prepared to spend more than you might normally.

A American restaurant while most of the foreign waiters and waitresses are well trained but the local waitress are just so impolite. A waitress came on request and in two second asking we whether I will place order. “你唔係叫野食咩？”  , the way the serve the food is like banging the table. I just cannot believe how terrible is their service. 
Food size is huge so better be noticed

開店後一直都想去試試，但是聽說排隊等很久所以就沒去了，這次終於去了，也大概等了30分鐘，不會太久，服務員帶位給了我們4個女生坐7-8人圓桌，旁邊的卡位有2張空的，想讓他們給我們換，他們問完一個又個，一個說不行一個說行，大概用了10分鐘才可以換，可能真的麻煩到他們的安排吧，謝謝。

真的要說他們食物的份量也算大份的，我們叫了意粉，小漢堡，炸蟹餅，牛排。食物很不錯，好吃，略貴，但質素好，上菜的服務員也很有禮貌，會主動問我們要不要什麼的。

最後飯後當然要來吃芝士蛋糕，我們每人一塊，都不同的，點了檸檬，咖啡，巧克力，紅絨。我們覺得咖啡和巧克力都太濃太甜，檸檬又太酸，紅絨剛剛好，下次應該吃原味試試，感覺會好吃。
